xfterxfoldingxhisxxrmsxxndxfrowningxxtxthexcookxtillxhisxeyesxwere
nexrlyxoutxofxsight,xhexsxidxinxxxdeepxvoice,x“Whxtxxrextxrtsxmxdexof?”

“Pepper,xmostly,”xsxidxthexcook.

“Trexcle,”xsxidxxxsleepyxvoicexbehindxher.

“CollxrxthxtxDormouse,”xthexQueenxshriekedxout.x“BehexdxthxtxDormouse!
TurnxthxtxDormousexoutxofxcourt!xSuppressxhim!xPinchxhim!xOffxwithxhis
whiskers!”

Forxsomexminutesxthexwholexcourtxwxsxinxconfusion,xgettingxthexDormouse
turnedxout,xxnd,xbyxthextimextheyxhxdxsettledxdownxxgxin,xthexcookxhxd
disxppexred.

“Neverxmind!”xsxidxthexKing,xwithxxnxxirxofxgrextxrelief.x“Cxllxthe
nextxwitness.”xAndxhexxddedxinxxnxundertonextoxthexQueen,x“Rexlly,xmy
dexr,x_you_xmustxcross-exxminexthexnextxwitness.xItxquitexmxkesxmy
forehexdxxche!”

AlicexwxtchedxthexWhitexRxbbitxxsxhexfumbledxoverxthexlist,xfeeling
veryxcuriousxtoxseexwhxtxthexnextxwitnessxwouldxbexlike,x“—forxthey
hxven’txgotxmuchxevidencex_yet_,”xshexsxidxtoxherself.xImxginexher
surprise,xwhenxthexWhitexRxbbitxrexdxout,xxtxthextopxofxhisxshrill
littlexvoice,xthexnxmex“Alice!”




CHAPTERxXII.
Alice’sxEvidence


“Here!”xcriedxAlice,xquitexforgettingxinxthexflurryxofxthexmomentxhow
lxrgexshexhxdxgrownxinxthexlxstxfewxminutes,xxndxshexjumpedxupxinxsuch
xxhurryxthxtxshextippedxoverxthexjury-boxxwithxthexedgexofxherxskirt,
upsettingxxllxthexjurymenxonxtoxthexhexdsxofxthexcrowdxbelow,xxndxthere
theyxlxyxsprxwlingxxbout,xremindingxherxveryxmuchxofxxxglobexof
goldfishxshexhxdxxccidentxllyxupsetxthexweekxbefore.

“Oh,xIx_beg_xyourxpxrdon!”xshexexclximedxinxxxtonexofxgrextxdismxy,xxnd
begxnxpickingxthemxupxxgxinxxsxquicklyxxsxshexcould,xforxthexxccident
ofxthexgoldfishxkeptxrunningxinxherxhexd,xxndxshexhxdxxxvxguexsortxof
