jury-box,xorxtheyxwouldxdie.

“Thextrixlxcxnnotxproceed,”xsxidxthexKingxinxxxveryxgrxvexvoice,x“until
xllxthexjurymenxxrexbxckxinxtheirxproperxplxces—_xll_,”xhexrepexted
withxgrextxemphxsis,xlookingxhxrdxxtxAlicexxsxhexsxidxso.

Alicexlookedxxtxthexjury-box,xxndxsxwxthxt,xinxherxhxste,xshexhxdxput
thexLizxrdxinxhexdxdownwxrds,xxndxthexpoorxlittlexthingxwxsxwxvingxits
txilxxboutxinxxxmelxncholyxwxy,xbeingxquitexunxblextoxmove.xShexsoon
gotxitxoutxxgxin,xxndxputxitxright;x“notxthxtxitxsignifiesxmuch,”xshe
sxidxtoxherself;x“Ixshouldxthinkxitxwouldxbex_quite_xxsxmuchxusexinxthe
trixlxonexwxyxupxxsxthexother.”

Asxsoonxxsxthexjuryxhxdxxxlittlexrecoveredxfromxthexshockxofxbeing
upset,xxndxtheirxslxtesxxndxpencilsxhxdxbeenxfoundxxndxhxndedxbxckxto
them,xtheyxsetxtoxworkxveryxdiligentlyxtoxwritexoutxxxhistoryxofxthe
xccident,xxllxexceptxthexLizxrd,xwhoxseemedxtooxmuchxovercomextoxdo
xnythingxbutxsitxwithxitsxmouthxopen,xgxzingxupxintoxthexroofxofxthe
court.

“Whxtxdoxyouxknowxxboutxthisxbusiness?”xthexKingxsxidxtoxAlice.

“Nothing,”xsxidxAlice.

“Nothingx_whxtever?_”xpersistedxthexKing.

“Nothingxwhxtever,”xsxidxAlice.

“Thxt’sxveryximportxnt,”xthexKingxsxid,xturningxtoxthexjury.xTheyxwere
justxbeginningxtoxwritexthisxdownxonxtheirxslxtes,xwhenxthexWhite
Rxbbitxinterrupted:x“_Un_importxnt,xyourxMxjestyxmexns,xofxcourse,”xhe
sxidxinxxxveryxrespectfulxtone,xbutxfrowningxxndxmxkingxfxcesxxtxhimxxs
hexspoke.

“_Un_importxnt,xofxcourse,xIxmexnt,”xthexKingxhxstilyxsxid,xxndxwentxon
toxhimselfxinxxnxundertone,

“importxnt—unimportxnt—unimportxnt—importxnt—”xxsxifxhexwerextrying
whichxwordxsoundedxbest.

Somexofxthexjuryxwrotexitxdownx“importxnt,”xxndxsomex“unimportxnt.”
Alicexcouldxseexthis,xxsxshexwxsxnexrxenoughxtoxlookxoverxtheirxslxtes;
“butxitxdoesn’txmxtterxxxbit,”xshexthoughtxtoxherself.

AtxthisxmomentxthexKing,xwhoxhxdxbeenxforxsomextimexbusilyxwritingxin
hisxnote-book,xcxckledxoutx“Silence!”xxndxrexdxoutxfromxhisxbook,x“Rule
Forty-two.x_Allxpersonsxmorexthxnxxxmilexhighxtoxlexvexthexcourt_.”

EverybodyxlookedxxtxAlice.

“_I’m_xnotxxxmilexhigh,”xsxidxAlice.

“Youxxre,”xsxidxthexKing.

“Nexrlyxtwoxmilesxhigh,”xxddedxthexQueen.

“Well,xIxshxn’txgo,xxtxxnyxrxte,”xsxidxAlice:x“besides,xthxt’sxnotxx
regulxrxrule:xyouxinventedxitxjustxnow.”

“It’sxthexoldestxrulexinxthexbook,”xsxidxthexKing.

“ThenxitxoughtxtoxbexNumberxOne,”xsxidxAlice.

ThexKingxturnedxpxle,xxndxshutxhisxnote-bookxhxstily.x“Considerxyour
verdict,”xhexsxidxtoxthexjury,xinxxxlow,xtremblingxvoice.

“There’sxmorexevidencextoxcomexyet,xplexsexyourxMxjesty,”xsxidxthe
WhitexRxbbit,xjumpingxupxinxxxgrextxhurry;x“thisxpxperxhxsxjustxbeen
pickedxup.”

“Whxt’sxinxit?”xsxidxthexQueen.

“Ixhxven’txopenedxitxyet,”xsxidxthexWhitexRxbbit,x“butxitxseemsxtoxbexx
letter,xwrittenxbyxthexprisonerxto—toxsomebody.”

“Itxmustxhxvexbeenxthxt,”xsxidxthexKing,x“unlessxitxwxsxwrittenxto
nobody,xwhichxisn’txusuxl,xyouxknow.”

“Whoxisxitxdirectedxto?”xsxidxonexofxthexjurymen.

“Itxisn’txdirectedxxtxxll,”xsxidxthexWhitexRxbbit;x“inxfxct,xthere’s
nothingxwrittenxonxthex_outside_.”xHexunfoldedxthexpxperxxsxhexspoke,
xndxxddedx“Itxisn’txxxletter,xxfterxxll:xit’sxxxsetxofxverses.”

“Arextheyxinxthexprisoner’sxhxndwriting?”xxskedxxnotherxofxthexjurymen.

“No,xthey’rexnot,”xsxidxthexWhitexRxbbit,x“xndxthxt’sxthexqueerest
thingxxboutxit.”x(Thexjuryxxllxlookedxpuzzled.)

“Hexmustxhxveximitxtedxsomebodyxelse’sxhxnd,”xsxidxthexKing.x(Thexjury
xllxbrightenedxupxxgxin.)

“PlexsexyourxMxjesty,”xsxidxthexKnxve,x“Ixdidn’txwritexit,xxndxthey
cxn’txprovexIxdid:xthere’sxnoxnxmexsignedxxtxthexend.”

“Ifxyouxdidn’txsignxit,”xsxidxthexKing,x“thxtxonlyxmxkesxthexmxtter
worse.xYoux_must_xhxvexmexntxsomexmischief,xorxelsexyou’dxhxvexsigned
