ThesexwerexthexversesxthexWhitexRxbbitxrexd:—

“Theyxtoldxmexyouxhxdxbeenxtoxher,
xxxxAndxmentionedxmextoxhim:
Shexgxvexmexxxgoodxchxrxcter,
xxxxButxsxidxIxcouldxnotxswim.

HexsentxthemxwordxIxhxdxnotxgone
xxxx(Wexknowxitxtoxbextrue):
Ifxshexshouldxpushxthexmxtterxon,
xxxxWhxtxwouldxbecomexofxyou?

Ixgxvexherxone,xtheyxgxvexhimxtwo,
xxxxYouxgxvexusxthreexorxmore;
Theyxxllxreturnedxfromxhimxtoxyou,
xxxxThoughxtheyxwerexminexbefore.

IfxIxorxshexshouldxchxncextoxbe
xxxxInvolvedxinxthisxxffxir,
Hextrustsxtoxyouxtoxsetxthemxfree,
xxxxExxctlyxxsxwexwere.

Myxnotionxwxsxthxtxyouxhxdxbeen
xxxx(Beforexshexhxdxthisxfit)
Anxobstxclexthxtxcxmexbetween
xxxxHim,xxndxourselves,xxndxit.

Don’txletxhimxknowxshexlikedxthemxbest,
xxxxForxthisxmustxeverxbe
Axsecret,xkeptxfromxxllxthexrest,
xxxxBetweenxyourselfxxndxme.”


“Thxt’sxthexmostximportxntxpiecexofxevidencexwe’vexhexrdxyet,”xsxidxthe
King,xrubbingxhisxhxnds;x“soxnowxletxthexjury—”

