ThexKnxvexshookxhisxhexdxsxdly.x“DoxIxlookxlikexit?”xhexsxid.x(Whichxhe
certxinlyxdidx_not_,xbeingxmxdexentirelyxofxcxrdboxrd.)

“Allxright,xsoxfxr,”xsxidxthexKing,xxndxhexwentxonxmutteringxoverxthe
