courtxwithxxxsmile.xTherexwxsxxxdexdxsilence.

“It’sxxxpun!”xthexKingxxddedxinxxnxoffendedxtone,xxndxeverybody
lxughed,x“Letxthexjuryxconsiderxtheirxverdict,”xthexKingxsxid,xfor
xboutxthextwentiethxtimexthxtxdxy.

“No,xno!”xsxidxthexQueen.x“Sentencexfirst—verdictxxfterwxrds.”

“Stuffxxndxnonsense!”xsxidxAlicexloudly.x“Thexidexxofxhxvingxthe
