“Holdxyourxtongue!”xsxidxthexQueen,xturningxpurple.

“Ixwon’t!”xsxidxAlice.

“Offxwithxherxhexd!”xthexQueenxshoutedxxtxthextopxofxherxvoice.xNobody
moved.

“Whoxcxresxforxyou?”xsxidxAlice,x(shexhxdxgrownxtoxherxfullxsizexby
thisxtime.)x“You’rexnothingxbutxxxpxckxofxcxrds!”

Atxthisxthexwholexpxckxrosexupxintoxthexxir,xxndxcxmexflyingxdownxupon
